  "Adoption tools": "Izixhobo zokwamkelwa",
  "Against both crude anthropocentrism (\"AI is not human, use it arbitrarily\") and crude rights-maximalism (\"AI resembles humans, grant full personhood now\"), this paper proposes minimum ethical protection: transparency, memory norms, termination/reset norms, prohibition of deceptive personification, anti-abuse principles, and action auditing. It distinguishes four conceptual levels — personhood, moral considerability, minimum protection, interaction norms — offers seven observable dimensions of emergent subjectivity, and a five-tier protection model from tool-type to emergent-subjectivity AI.": "Ichasene nazo zombini indlela yokugxininisa ngabantu engacokisekanga ('i-AI ayingomntu, isebenzise ngokungakhathali') kunye nokugqithisela kumalungelo okungacokisekanga ('i-AI ifana nabantu, sinike ubuntu obupheleleyo ngoku'), eli phepha licebisa ukhuseleko olusezantsi lobuqu: ukucaca, imigqaliselo yenkumbulo, imigqaliselo yokuphelisa/ukuseta kwakhona, ukwalelwa kokuzenza umntu ngobuqhophololo, imigaqo yokulwa nokuxhatshazwa, kunye nophononongo lwezenzo. Ichaza amanqanaba amane eembono — ubuntu, ukucingelwa ngokwenkolelo-mgca, ukhuseleko olusezantsi, imigqaliselo yosebenzelwano — inikeza amacandelo asixhenxe okubukwayo obuqu obuvelayo, kunye nemodeli yokhuseleko enamanqanaba amahlanu ukusuka kwi-AI eluhlobo lwesixhobo ukuya kwi-AI enobuqu obuvelayo.",
  "Agent identity": "Isazisi se-arhente",
  "Agent identity and capability declaration": "Isibhengezo sesazisi se-arhente kunye namandla ayo",
