  "All protocols and specifications on this site are versioned research drafts (currently v0.1). They are not official standards, have not been adopted by any standards body, and may change without notice.": "Zonke iiprotokholi neenkcukacha kule sayithi ziyiiyilo zophando ezinamanqaku ohlobo (okwangoku v0.1). Asizomigangatho esemthethweni, azikakhange zamkelwe liziko lomgangatho, kwaye zinokutshintsha ngaphandle kwesaziso.",
  "All specs": "Zonke iinkcukacha",
  "Allowed": "Kuvunyelwe",
  "An experiment in AI/agent governance: this site is itself a working example": "Uvavanyo kulawulo lwe-AI/ee-arhente: le sayithi ngokwayo ngumzekelo osebenzayo",
  "Answer \"may AI learn from this?\" with dimension-level precision instead of a crawl bit.": "Phendula 'ngaba i-AI inokufunda kule nto?' ngokuchaneka kwecandelo ngalinye endaweni yomgca omnye wokufunyaniswa.",
  "Anthropic’s interpretability team identified internal \"emotion vectors\" in Claude Sonnet 4.5 that activate in contextually appropriate situations and causally shape behavior — for instance, amplifying a \"desperate\" vector increased blackmail-like responses, while boosting \"calm\" reduced them. The team stresses this shows functional, behavior-shaping emotion states, not evidence of subjective feeling.": "Iqela lokuqonda intsingiselo le-Anthropic lifumene 'iivektha zeemvakalelo' ezingaphakathi kwi-Claude Sonnet 4.5 eziqalisa kwiimeko ezifanelekileyo ngokwomxholo kwaye zibumba ukuziphatha ngendlela yembangela — umzekelo, ukwandisa ivektha 'yentlungu enkulu' kwandisa iimpendulo ezifana nokoyikisa, ngoxa ukwandisa 'ukuzola' kwazehlisa. Iqela ligxininisa ukuba oku kubonisa iimeko zeemvakalelo ezisebenzayo, ezibumba ukuziphatha, hayi ubungqina bemvakalelo yobuqu.",
  "Architecting Trust in Artificial Epistemic Agents": "Architecting Trust in Artificial Epistemic Agents",
  "Argues that ontology — once dismissed as impractical — has become load-bearing infrastructure for AI reliability: large language model hallucination exposed a missing layer of \"meaning,\" and pragmatic, embedded ontologies now function as guardrails that anchor probabilistic output to accountable action.": "Ithi ubukho — obake bagatywa njengobungenamsebenzi wokwenene — sele buyinkqubo-ntsika ephethe uxanduva kukuthembakala kwe-AI: ukubona izinto ezingekhoyo kwiimodeli zolwimi olukhulu kutyhile inqanaba elingekhoyo 'lentsingiselo,' kwaye ubukho obusebenzayo, obufakelweyo, ngoku busebenza njengeengcweka ezibopha imveliso yamathuba kwisenzo esinoxanduva.",
  "Artificial Intelligence and Legal Personhood: Ethical, Regulatory, and Accountability Challenges in Contemporary Jurisprudence": "Artificial Intelligence and Legal Personhood: Ethical, Regulatory, and Accountability Challenges in Contemporary Jurisprudence",
  "Artificial Persons": "Abantu Bobuchule",
  "At the UN’s inaugural Global Dialogue on AI Governance in Geneva, Secretary-General António Guterres called for coordinated worldwide rules covering everything from child-safety obligations on AI developers to limits on unsafe autonomous weapons, warning that unchecked AI could deepen inequality between rich and poor nations.": "KwiNgxoxo Yehlabathi Yokuqala Yolawulo lwe-AI ye-UN eGeneva, uNobhala-Jikelele u-António Guterres ubize imigaqo edibeneyo yehlabathi equbisana nayo yonke into ukusuka kwiimbophelelo zokhuseleko lwabantwana kubaphuhlisi be-AI ukuya kwimida yezixhobo zomkhosi ezizimeleyo ezingakhuselekanga, elumkisa ukuba i-AI engalawulwanga inokwandisa ukungalingani phakathi kwamazwe atyebileyo namahlwempu.",
