  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Imizekelo yekhowudi, iiSkim ze-JSON, kunye neetemplate zomgaqo ezifundwa yimatshini zinikwe ilayisensi phantsi kwe-MIT License ngaphandle kokuba kuchaziwe ngokwahlukileyo. Ungazisebenzisa ngokukhululekileyo kwiisayithi zakho.",
