  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "Guqula izibhengezo zamalungelo zibe yimarike yelayisensi esebenzayo endaweni yewebhu enomgca omnye ovulekileyo/ovaliweyo.",
