  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Umboniso wemfundo: i-HMAC-SHA256 enemfihlelo eyabelwanayo, ebonisa iitokheni zelayisensi ezibotshelelwe kwisicelo, eziphelelwa lixesha, ezinokuqinisekiswa. Iitokheni zemveliso zifanele zisayinwe ngokungalingani, ngesitshixo esidlangalaleni sompapashi esinokufunyanwa phantsi kwe-/.well-known/.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Amanye amanqaku esibhozo kwi-/topics, ngeli xesha ephandwe yi-arhente ye-AI endaweni yokuhlelwa ngesandla — umgaqo ofanayo njengangaphambili: umthombo ngamnye ufunyenwe kwaye waqinisekiswa ephila, iimfingo ziyimfingo yethu yokwenene, ngaphambi kokuba nantoni na yongezwe. Amanqaku ali-14 esewonke.",
