  "English edition →": "Uhlelo lwesiNgesi →",
  "Ensure openness is machine-executable — so goodwill is not discarded as legal uncertainty.": "Qinisekisa ukuba ukuvuleleka kunokusetyenziswa yimatshini — ukuze intando entle ingalahlwa njengokungaqiniseki ngokomthetho.",
