  "Turns declared rights into executable licensing: quote, pay, verify, audit, revoke.": "Iguqula amalungelo abhengeziweyo abe lilayisensi enokusetyenziswa: ukucacisa ixabiso, ukuhlawula, ukuqinisekisa, uphononongo, ukurhoxisa.",
  "Twenty languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Greek, Italian, Dutch.": "Kukho iilwimi ezingamashumi amabini eziphilayo ngokupheleleyo: isiNgesi, isiTshayina Sendabuko, isiTshayina Esilula, isiJapan, isiKorea, isiFrentshi, isiJamani, isiPanish, isiPhuthukezi, isiRashiya, isiArabhu, isiTurkey, isiPersi, isiBengali, isiHindi, isiIndonesia, isiVietnam, isiGrike, isiTaliyane, isiDatshi.",
  "Two license tiers: a free public tier and a contact-based commercial tier.": "Amanqanaba amabini elayisensi: inqanaba lasidlangalala elisimahla kunye nenqanaba lorhwebo elisekelwe kunxibelelwano.",
  "UI": "Ujongano Lomsebenzisi",
  "Undefined openness reads as legal uncertainty to AI pipelines and gets cleaned out; only protocolized, machine-readable permission makes content genuinely learnable.": "Ukuvuleleka okungachazwanga kufundwa njengokungaqiniseki ngokomthetho kwiinkqubo ze-AI kwaye kuyasuswa; yimvume kuphela eqinisekiswa ziiprotokholi, efundwa yimatshini, eyenza umxholo ufundeke ngokwenene.",
  "Usage logs and audit trails": "Iirekhodi zokusetyenziswa kunye nemikhondo yohlolo-mfihlo",
