  "Validator": "Validator",
  "Verified dataset markets and collective licensing": "Iimarike zeesethi zedatha eziqinisekisiweyo kunye nelayisensi yesizwe",
  "Verified in both LTR and RTL contexts: the panel mirrors correctly for Arabic and Persian without any special-casing, using logical CSS positioning.": "Kuqinisekisiwe kuzo zombini iimeko, i-LTR ne-RTL: ipaneli izibonakalisa ngokuchanekileyo kwisiArabhu nesiPersi ngaphandle kwayo nayiphi na indlela ekhethekileyo, isebenzisa ukubekwa kwe-CSS yesengqiqo.",
  "Verify": "Qinisekisa",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts.": "Imbali yohlobo yale sayithi kunye neeyilo zayo zeeprotokholi.",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts. Breaking spec changes are recorded here.": "Imbali yohlobo yale sayithi kunye neeyilo zayo zeeprotokholi. Iinguqu eziphula iinkcukacha zirekhodwa apha.",
  "Versioned specifications, JSON Schemas, and the policy files actually deployed on this site. Every file can be downloaded, validated, and cited directly.": "Iinkcukacha ezinamanqaku ohlobo, iiSkim ze-JSON, kunye neefayile zomgaqo ezibekwe ngokwenene kule sayithi. Ifayile nganye inokukhutshelwa, iqinisekiswe, kwaye icaphulwe ngokuthe ngqo.",
  "Versioning": "Ukumiselwa Kwamanqaku Ohlobo",
  "Versions": "Iinguqulelo",
  "Video and audio companions to the protocols and papers — the AI rights layer, watchable and listenable.": "Iividiyo nemisindo ehambelana neeprotokholi namaphepha — inqanaba lamalungelo e-AI, elinokubukelwa nokumamelwa.",
  "Videos": "Iividiyo",
  "Want to generate your own policy file?": "Ufuna ukuvelisa ifayile yakho yomgaqo?",
  "Web fonts are loaded from Google Fonts, which receives standard font requests from your browser. No other third-party scripts are used.": "Iifonti zewebhu zilayishwa kwi-Google Fonts, efumana izicelo eziqhelekileyo zefonti kwisikhangeli sakho. Akukho zinye izikripthi zabantu besithathu ezisetyenzisiweyo.",
  "What AI systems may do with content: read, summarize, transform, retrieve, train, commercialize, redistribute. The AICR ruleset and the AICL licensing layer make these rights declarable and transactable.": "Oko iinkqubo ze-AI zinokukwenza ngomxholo: ukufunda, ukushwankathela, ukuguqula, ukufunyanisa, ukuqeqesha, ukwenza ngokorhwebo, ukusasaza kwakhona. Uluhlu lwemigaqo ye-AICR kunye nenqanaba lelayisensi ye-AICL zenza la malungelo abhengezeke kwaye enziwe ngentengiselwano.",
  "What a server can return when an AI crawler requests licensed content without a license token — a machine-actionable quote instead of a dead end.": "Oko iseva inokukubuyisela xa i-crawler ye-AI icela umxholo onelayisensi ngaphandle kwetokheni yelayisensi — ixabiso elinokusetyenziswa yimatshini endaweni yendlela engenampendulo.",
  "What this site is": "Le sayithi iyintoni",
  "What this site is not": "Le sayithi ayiyontoni",
  "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration": "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration",
  "Whether AI may learn, to what depth, for which purposes, and under what obligations. Being read is not being learned from; \"not prohibited\" is not \"learnable\". AIRS and AILP turn learning permission into a graduated, machine-readable spectrum.": "Enoba i-AI inokufunda, kubunzulu obunjani, ngeenjongo ezinjani, kunye nangaphantsi kweembophelelo ezinjani. Ukufundwa akukho njengokufundelwa kuko; 'ukungathintelwa' akukho njengoko kuthiwa 'kunokufundwa.' I-AIRS kunye ne-AILP ziguqula imvume yokufunda ibe luluhlu olunyukayo, olufundwa yimatshini.",
  "Whitepapers": "Amaphepha Amhlophe",
  "Whitepapers & Docs": "Amaphepha Amhlophe Namaxwebhu",
  "Whitepapers remain English-first by design; machine-readable files stay language-neutral.": "Amaphepha amhlophe ahlala eqala ngesiNgesi ngokoyilo; iifayile ezifundwa yimatshini zihlala zingathathi cala ngolwimi.",
  "Who is behind it": "Ngubani osemva kwayo",
  "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections": "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections",
  "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics": "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics",
  "Why a single allow/deny bit cannot govern AI-era content use — and what a rights layer looks like instead.": "Kutheni umgca omnye wokuvuma/ukwala ungenakulawula ukusetyenziswa komxholo kwixesha le-AI — kwaye injani inqanaba lamalungelo endaweni yaloo nto.",
  "Why undefined openness gets cleaned out of training pipelines": "Kutheni ukuvuleleka okungachazwanga kususwa kwiinkqubo zoqeqesho",
  "Wilks, Ladak, and Loughnan (University of Edinburgh) argue that philosophical debate over AI consciousness overlooks psychological research on animal ethics — the same cognitive and social biases that limit moral consideration for animals will likely limit it for AI too, regardless of whether AI ever becomes conscious.": "UWilks, uLadak, noLoughnan (baseYunivesithi yaseEdinburgh) bathi ingxoxo yefilosofi malunga nokuphaphama kwengqondo kwe-AI iyalibala uphando lwengqondo malunga nemilinganiselo yokuziphatha kwizilwanyana — ezona ziphosiso zengqondo nezentlalo ezithintela ukucingelwa ngokwemilinganiselo yokuziphatha kwizilwanyana ziya kuthintela nakwi-AI, nokuba i-AI ingaze iphaphame na ingqondo okanye hayi.",
  "You are leaving AGIRight.org": "Uyaphuma kwi-AGIRight.org",
