  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "'AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer' ngoku ipapashiwe ngesiNgesi njengohlelo olusemthethweni; umbhalo wokuqala wesiTshayina uyahlala ufumaneka kwaye zombini iinguqulelo ziyanxulumana.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "'Protocolized Openness' iqinisekisiwe njengephepha lolwimi lwesiNgesi (elinemibhalo efanayo ecalulwa yisiTshayina) — akukho nguqulelo yahlukileyo icwangcisiweyo.",
